0.title: Jimi Junior Figures It Out (WIP)
0.plot: Erin Century creates a time machine and she leaps back 25 years to when she was 12 and gets help to change the Present from her 8 year old brother Jimi Junior and her 13 year old former boyfriend, Beau. Comedy ensues and the story begins.

imdb.plot outline: Quarter Century GIRL. A Sci-Fi Comedy series created in which the genius character, Erin Century invents time travel at 37 years old. She leaps back (and forth) from the Present to 25 years into the Past when she was 12 to correct what once went wrong with the help of her former boyfriend Beau and her eccentric brother Jimi Junior. Comedic successes and chaos ensue.
